* Will currently only work with PostgreSQL, don't be fooled by the use of PDO...
* SQL creation script(s) are in sql/

* Copy inc/config.php.dist to inc/config.php and change the 'secret' value!
* You will need to manually insert your first user.

The AGPLv3 prohibits running modified versions without providing the source code,
the inc/config.php file is not considered part of a derivative work providing that
the inc/config.php.dist file is also kept up to date. A GNU makefile is included to
aid creation of an archive.
